===Pronunciation===
עמר / ‛âmar / aw-mar'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''עמר'''

# Properly, apparently to [[heap]]; figuratively to chastise (as if piling blows); specifically (as denominative from {{HH|6016}}) to gather grain: - bind sheaves, make merchandise of.

